937f2ee96c9172e9b95fe40ce37e728eb4a","tid":1557451,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:22:29.000Z","msg":"根據香港法例217章《武器條例》第4條，任何人管有違禁武器，均屬犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例217章《武器條例》，違禁武器包括:<br />\n<br />\n中國式飛鏢<br />\n<br />\n重力刀<br />\n<br />\n重力操作鋼棒<br />\n<br />\n指節套，不論是否有尖釘及是否有刀刃<br />\n<br />\n附有手柄的鐵鏈<br />\n<br />\n彈簧鋼棒<br />\n<br />\n任何以彈簧或其他機械或電動裝置露出刀刃的刀<br />\n<br />\n任何有刀刃或尖端的武器，其設計是在使用時以拳頭緊握手柄，而刀刃或尖端則從拳頭指縫間突出<br />\n<br />\n伸縮警棍屬重力操作鋼棒，雖然報警無用。但唔攞出黎，只收喺袋內面都犯法。"},{"pid":"f071c18240e238849f2688af63b0e274b1670b9a","tid":1557451,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"阿蛇我支持你, 支棍點賣法?"},{"pid":"0b44c3905a1bd7e17b10b610b0aed4d1ccdf65a4","tid":1557451,"uid":6261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:23:51.000Z","msg":"真 圍屌冇用 圍毆先有用"},{"pid":"5ab1eec35eb0cf703115c5837e2e3e008c3bf221","tid":1557451,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f6f7341c82f5bf709d886d4ddbe76346d6c8c2","tid":1557451,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"如果打死人, 你估美國會點制裁黑警"},{"pid":"d35d3035dc3f0af12cf12cd460b9ba5c4cb7ab43","tid":1557451,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:25:56.000Z","msg":"只可以走 就算比你反擊左都比黑警有藉口上門拉人<br />\n肯定會再check你示威果陣在唔在場"},{"pid":"1e4caa232db788f099845ada9d5fce493214e752","tid":1557451,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"P 俾超額發唔到Post，please help <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9.15 係「國際民主日」，點解完全無活動Post? </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據《世界人權宣言》第二十一條第（三）款﹕「人民的意志是政府權力的基礎」<br />\n9.15係聯合國嘅「國際民主日」，2019年主題「參與」，重申民主係「以人為中心」。(官網﹕<a href=\"https://www.un.org/zh/events/democracyday/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fzh%2Fevents%2Fdemocracyday%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=fc91bd9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.un.org/zh/events/democracyday/</a> (得殘體字sorry) ) <br />\n<br />\n我哋依定係對抗緊極權，爭取緊雙普選，呢個咁有象徵意義嘅日子點可以唔做嘢? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本地應該要搞大遊行，本來民陣前兩日都話申請緊</span>，但警方唔回應就完全無哂聲氣。<span style=\"color: red;\">海外集會要再次港、藏、疆合作</span>，甚至聯繫埋全世界受壓迫地區嘅人一齊發聲。<br />\n<br />\n6.12、721、811、831&hellip;全部都要勝利之後先可以查明真相，如果唔係有再多嘅證據，未來都只會變成野史。請大家化憤怒為創意同行動吧！世界領袖讚賞我哋嘅，係呢場運動嘅靈活多變，不忘同世界連軌。而我地亦已成功將呢場運動變成<span style=\"color: red;\">自由世界VS極權嘅抗爭</span>。我哋唔想成為國際怨婦，就要令更加多人明白This is <span style=\"color: red;\">NOT ONLY a protest for Hong Kong people but for the sake of the World! </span><br />\n<br />\nAttention! 依家正苦係咁用衝突黎分化我哋同世界建立既信任。請大家要好小心好小心好小心好小心好小心好小心! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Free Hong Kong <br />\nAnti Chinazi </span></span><br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n1. 之前有巴打寫﹕If we burn, the world burns  有無人留咗record ? <br />\n2. 回顧9.4 「2019年中美關係回顧」聽證會<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-09-05/70001880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-09-05%2F70001880&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=f7991324\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-09-05/70001880</a>"},{"pid":"0f3e081b00061f127440dc49e736fbc2d56057f9","tid":1557451,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1bf591dcbd900cdc00d9f1761fe5a7c650f9bd","tid":1557451,"uid":175119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"最慘你想還拖嗰時仲有班左膠喺度話唔好打<br />\n跟住繼續俾人打再拉埋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"巴打不論言論定user名都咁有taste <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49f78a9ea4f3732f32af6c575751f8f2ffb400a","tid":1557451,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0