0倍更有效吸收<br />\n就咁飲太高糖唔吸收<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\nHerbalife  健康教練<br />\n唔係重點 重點係大家強身健體<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民皆兵</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n我要所有人隨時隨地可以極速轉場<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地可以更團結 去改變香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衝衝子走得快<br />\n哨兵Be Water <br />\nFirst aid 補給 <br />\n全世界只有你可以有能力保護自己同記者<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需 要TG 唔問名 <br />\n同你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n如果想做下運動放鬆<br />\n歡迎黎搵我做下運動 <br />\n有街頭健身<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"ce5c37741c25785f6701fa1d4c0e3adf4aac9b87","tid":1557451,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b21fd17004a1b326b7cb34a69afdd4b707d7ec6c","tid":1557451,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97dfcd0ae429619a61b0e630deb99047beb0c006","tid":1557451,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"217eee6fee1567ea53fdf4f798514edb00ad53ed","tid":1557451,"uid":242537,"like":77,"dislike":3,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EEFMxXsUEAAIH5r?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEEFMxXsUEAAIH5r%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=4baceee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedB